{"tid":2067530,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"「香港地產」— 香港蟬聯全球樓價最高城市","createTime":"2020-06-17T05:20:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-17T07:09:01.000Z","uid":360266,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"23bcf035373b51e88bab0e43162251a64921eda4","tid":2067530,"uid":360266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T05:20:03.000Z","msg":"香港蟬聯全球樓價最高城市<br />\n[28Hse 三地產焦點 第二百七十四期 2020年6月17日]<br />\n<br />\n眾所周知，香港樓價多年來一直處於巔峰狀態，不時見到二手破頂成交的新聞。市場每次公布關於樓市的報告，香港都是在全世界名列前茅，是世界數一數二高樓價的地區。<br />\n <br />\n世邦魏理仕早前公布《2020全球生活報告》，在全球39個重點城市的住宅市場數據與發展趨勢進行分析，報告顯示樓價最高的十大城市中有一半位於亞洲，當中香港更是蟬聯全球樓價最高城市。<br />\n <br />\n究竟香港樓價有幾貴呢？根據報告，以7.8港元兌1美元來計算，香港去年平均樓價高達約$978.1萬（125.4萬美元），平均呎價約$1.55萬（1,987美元），升幅4.7%，繼續高居全球之首。<br />\n <br />\n第二位是德國城市慕尼黑，平均樓價約$780萬（$100萬美元），平均呎價為約$6,404（821美元）；第三位則是新加坡，平均樓價約$713.7萬（91.5萬美元），平均呎價$9,469（1,214美元）。"},{"pid":"c9130fb26c4c0f8444c0108b1f2de57bd673463d","tid":2067530,"uid":22422,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T05:23:11.000Z","msg":"第二嗰個車尾燈都見唔到<br />\n支那臭港又贏<br />\n又考第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"389c104a8166457f1afc13322ed77ef883b69241","tid":2067530,"uid":159313,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T05:26:16.000Z","msg":"唔係第一先係新聞ok?"},{"pid":"67c2c8858c724b02c265cce148efcd772c741126","tid":2067530,"uid":343361,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T05:31:14.000Z","msg":"大家幫幫手再炒高啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做宇宙最強"},{"pid":"d31ac8991ecf55a906addbac0695ef4d6b8cc40e","tid":2067530,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T06:24:32.000Z","msg":"唔應該叻既野&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e0a3819dd36366f94ee1a1a77c93eb6f6f70c21","tid":2067530,"uid":215249,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T06:28:16.000Z","msg":"研究顯示樓價的價格同當地人既人品質素成反比"},{"pid":"917f951bc0da1aaa31df486dd38625e087f9dac5","tid":2067530,"uid":100045,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T06:33:10.000Z","msg":"好波！繼續奴役香港人"},{"pid":"94b1908e72666b4915cea0933142f3d6d2237ba4","tid":2067530,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T06:36:44.000Z","msg":"樓市高高高<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fafd2b779f9c58abf9dbf67ad2d0128bcb5a8fb","tid":2067530,"uid":352734,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T07:09:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}